<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>Leymah Gbowee</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/1403?language=en' lang='en'>
Unlock the intelligence, passion, greatness of girls
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
