<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:46
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='335000' id='t-335000'>Several years ago, a few friends of mine</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='338000' id='t-338000'>decided we needed to bridge the disconnect</span>
