<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='342000' id='t-342000'>and the generation of young women.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='344000' id='t-344000'>It's not enough to say</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='346000' id='t-346000'>you have two Nobel laureates from the Republic of Liberia</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='349000' id='t-349000'>when your girls' kids are totally out there</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='352000' id='t-352000'>and no hope, or seemingly no hope.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='355000' id='t-355000'>We created a space</span>
